		"description": "<p>You gain proficiency with the Religion skill and gain the skill specialty of your choice of cults or prophecy.</p>\n<p>You also gain proficiency with the History skill and gain the skill specialty of either legends or genealogy.</p>\n<p>You also learn the following spells at the following levels, and they do not count against your spells known:</p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 83.9845px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 24.7031%;\"><col style=\"width: 75.2969%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\"><strong>1st Level</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\"><em>faerie fire</em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\"><strong>2nd Level</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\"><em>moonbeam</em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\"><strong>3rd Level</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\"><em>venomous succor</em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\"><strong>4th Level</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\"><em>banishment</em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\"><strong>5th Level</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\"><em>hallow</em></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
